        "content": "<p>Is there a command similiar to <code>#check</code> that also simplifies the type, possibly with <code>simp</code>?</p>",
        "id": 478360382,
        "sender_full_name": "Chris Henson",
        "timestamp": 1729628111
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Is <code>#simp ...</code> a thing?</p>",
        "id": 478360683,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1729628259
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Tactic/Conv.html#Mathlib.Tactic.Conv.%C2%ABcommand#simpOnly_=%3E__%C2%BB\">docs#Mathlib.Tactic.Conv.«command#simpOnly_=&gt;__»</a>, maybe?</p>",
        "id": 478360883,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1729628334
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yes, but it only simplifies the expression. It does not infer the type. <code>#simp %type_of your_thing</code> should do</p>",
        "id": 478360941,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1729628368
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ah, I had missed \"simplifying the <em>type</em>\"!</p>",
        "id": 478361101,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1729628417
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yael's code has a small typo. This works:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Tactic</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">type_of</span><span class=\"bp\">%</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">true</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 478361726,
        "sender_full_name": "Floris van Doorn",
        "timestamp": 1729628681
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Argh, I was trying really hard to remember which side the <code>%</code> went on <span aria-label=\"see no evil\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f648\" role=\"img\" title=\"see no evil\">:see_no_evil:</span></p>",
        "id": 478362247,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1729628888
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>No worries, I figured it out. Thanks!</p>",
        "id": 478362281,
        "sender_full_name": "Chris Henson",
        "timestamp": 1729628911
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It should go where a percentage would go, right?</p>",
