        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"321459\">Damiano Testa</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/270676-lean4/topic/combined.20check.20and.20simp.20command/near/478362309\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It should go where a percentage would go, right?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Well actually I thought it went at the start because no Lean identifier can start with it</p>",
