    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"lol\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f606\" role=\"img\" title=\"lol\">:lol:</span>   I had not thought of yours, so I simply went for where I would expect the symbol to go:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>my first reaction to <code>#</code> is a cardinality and I place it before the object, </li>\n<li>my first reaction to <code>%</code> is a percentage and I place it after the object.</li>\n</ul>",
        "id": 478363206,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1729629258
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>With <code>#</code> I think \"time to start a command\" and with <code>%</code> I think \"oh right, this was a special elaborator\"</p>",
